PrecisEnactment of an ORDER RESPECTING THE WITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL OF CERTAIN LANDS IN THE YUKON TERRITORY (DdHAW GHRO HABITAT PROTECTION AREA, Y.T.) - which (a) provides for the withdrawal from disposal of a number of tracts of land in the Yukon Territory, until August 31, 2005, and (b) repeals the Withdrawal from Disposal Order (Ddhaw Ghro Habitat Protection Area, Y.T.), made by Order in Council P.C. 1997-1189.
